 This TV was developed by Icube Research Institute 

00:00:14.240 --> 00:00:16.100
 Using ICC (Integrated Cognitive Creation) technology 

00:00:16.100 --> 00:00:20.590
 It occurs when a human looks at a real scene or subject directly 

00:00:20.590 --> 00:00:22.890
 Experience equivalent to cognitive work 

00:00:22.890 --> 00:00:24.820
 What can be obtained when watching a video 

00:00:24.820 --> 00:00:27.020
 The purpose is 

00:00:27.020 --> 00:00:31.380
 I really want to see this feeling of depth 

