 Normally you enter from here 

00:00:33.070 --> 00:00:34.230
 Climb up all the way up 

00:00:34.230 --> 00:00:36.329
 You can see the way to go 

00:00:36.329 --> 00:00:37.820
 Then, here is the distance 

00:00:37.820 --> 00:00:41.460
 Maybe not go about 100 meters 

00:00:41.460 --> 00:00:42.650
 I do not go to there 

00:00:42.650 --> 00:00:44.480
 You can see the bridge instantly 

00:00:44.480 --> 00:00:46.370
 When you say why you understand 

00:00:46.370 --> 00:00:48.120
 Because the eyes scan 

00:00:48.120 --> 00:00:50.260
 From this bridge to here 

00:00:50.260 --> 00:00:52.940
 Go to the stairs, dive and climb 

00:00:52.940 --> 00:00:54.710
 When you scan your eyes 

00:00:54.710 --> 00:00:59.050
 Each position has the correct resolution 

00:00:59.050 --> 00:01:00.620
 As it is not so with a camera 

00:01:00.620 --> 00:01:02.250
 If the focus is on somewhere 

00:01:02.250 --> 00:01:04.320
 There is a lot of bandwidth there 

00:01:04.320 --> 00:01:07.110
 There is no sense of distance if there are no more 

00:01:07.110 --> 00:01:08.409
 Because it is bad 

00:01:08.409 --> 00:01:11.500
 I want to do the next 

00:01:11.500 --> 00:01:16.200
 This time somehow from the incoming electrical signal 

00:01:16.200 --> 00:01:20.000
 The original real world light signal 

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:23.179
 I want to create a technology to replace video 

00:01:23.179 --> 00:01:27.090
 The video released this time is the video taken with a high-definition camera 

00:01:27.090 --> 00:01:30.100
 Although up-converted to 4K resolution 

00:01:30.100 --> 00:01:33.510
 High resolution video and noise reduction 

00:01:33.510 --> 00:01:36.390
 Not only conventional super resolution technology 

00:01:36.390 --> 00:01:38.750
 Perspective and three-dimensional 

00:01:38.750 --> 00:01:43.590
 It is something to be recognized in a form closer to nature 

